      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "VISTA YANK (1) was in the placings last time but shapes well for this on her slick win the start prior, getting around this track over 461m in 25.94. Has the ability and looks hard to top. TRICK (3) below best last time at this track (26.17) in a Grade 3, finishing a 5 length fourth. Makes strong appeal on best. AUNTY MEDIO (8) should get a clear run from the wide draw. Safely held last start when a 16 length 8th at Launceston (31.06). Form here at this distance is strong including two wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings four times from six starts. Cannot be left out. POP'S GIRL (6) cannot be underestimated.",
